longBusinessSummary: Hawkeye Systems, Inc. engages in the distribution, importation, and sale of Personal Protective Equipment (PPE) and other medical devices. Its PPE products include masks, gowns, sanitizer, and ventilators. The company was incorporated in 2018 and is based in Savannah, Georgia.
